ygData.msgSnippet: Thanks for the review, Tina. Good to hear from you again. Hope you are well. (For those who don t know, Tina is the founder of EQ_Rainbow.) As to EQ burnout,
ygData.messageBody:
Thanks for the review, Tina. Good to hear from you again. Hope you are well.
(For those who don't know, Tina is the founder of EQ_Rainbow.)

As to EQ burnout, been there, done that. I'm very happy now that I've come
back because the guild on Rodcet is so much fun and is really growing. It
seems like we've averaged one new person per day so far this month. Everyone
is also very helpful, giving stuff to the new people and helping them out.

David
(Kerik, Wood Elf Druid)
